#: ../../T/test.rst:10
msgid ""
"Real users bashing on a prototype long enough to get thoroughly acquainted "
"with it, with careful monitoring and followup of the results."
msgstr "本物のユーザーがプロトタイプを、それに十分に慣れ親しむまで長い間叩き回ること。結果の注意深い監視と追跡を伴う。"

#: ../../T/test.rst:13
msgid ""
"Some bored random user trying a couple of the simpler features with a "
"developer looking over his or her shoulder, ready to pounce on mistakes."
msgstr "退屈した適当なユーザーが、開発者が肩越しに見守り間違いに飛びかかろうと身構える中で、より単純な機能のいくつかを試すこと。"

#: ../../T/test.rst:15
msgid ""
"Judging by the quality of most software, the second definition is far more "
"prevalent. See also :ref:`demo`\\."
msgstr "ほとんどのソフトウェアの質から判断すると、二つ目の定義の方がはるかに普及している。\\ :ref:`demo`\\ も参照。"
